HEADWORD: Purposedly
<hw>Pur"posed*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a purposed
manner; according to purpose or design; purposely.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A poem composed <qex>purposedly</qex> of the Trojan war.
<qex>Holland</qex>.</q>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Purposeful</ent>⟦br⟧
